  BNP Paribas ,  France ’s largest bank,
met with  South Africa ’s banking regulator yesterday to exchange
information about operating in the country.  Standard Bank Group Ltd. may sell its stake in Russia’s  Troika Dialog , Johannesburg’s Business Day newspaper said,
citing Renaissance Capital and Russian media reports. The
company is a minority shareholder in Troika and has a “strong
interest” in  Russia  as a region, Simon Ridley, the company’s
finance director, said in an interview with Bloomberg News.  To contact the reporter on this story:
